select count(*) as aggregate from `personal` left join (
SELECT
pers_id,
sum(d1530478800) as d1530478800,sum(d1530565200) as d1530565200,sum(d1530651600) as d1530651600,sum(d1530738000) as d1530738000,sum(d1530824400) as d1530824400,sum(d1530910800) as d1530910800,sum(d1530997200) as d1530997200,sum(d1531083600) as d1531083600,sum(d1531170000) as d1531170000,sum(d1531256400) as d1531256400,sum(d1531342800) as d1531342800
FROM (
SELECT
pers_id,
IF(date = '2018-07-02', sum, null) as d1530478800,IF(date = '2018-07-03', sum, null) as d1530565200,IF(date = '2018-07-04', sum, null) as d1530651600,IF(date = '2018-07-05', sum, null) as d1530738000,IF(date = '2018-07-06', sum, null) as d1530824400,IF(date = '2018-07-07', sum, null) as d1530910800,IF(date = '2018-07-08', sum, null) as d1530997200,IF(date = '2018-07-09', sum, null) as d1531083600,IF(date = '2018-07-10', sum, null) as d1531170000,IF(date = '2018-07-11', sum, null) as d1531256400,IF(date = '2018-07-12', sum, null) as d1531342800
FROM (
SELECT
sum(worktime) as sum,
pers_id,
date
FROM personal_times
WHERE date BETWEEN '2018-07-02' AND '2018-07-12'
GROUP BY pers_id, date
) as pt
) as st
group by pers_id) as at on `at`.`pers_id` = `personal`.`pers_id` where `is_active` = '1' group by `personal`.`id`
